tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE community_demographics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(100),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  occupation VARCHAR(50),
  address TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE outreach_programs (
    program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    target_population INT NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);
CREATE TABLE community_members (   member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,   first_name VARCHAR(255),   last_name VARCHAR(255),   age INT,   gender VARCHAR(10) );
CREATE TABLE outreach_programs (   program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,   program_name VARCHAR(255),   start_date DATE,   end_date DATE,   coordinator_name VARCHAR(255) );

CREATE TABLE program_attendance (   attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,   member_id INT,   program_id INT,   attendance_date DATE,   attended BOOLEAN,   FOREIGN KEY (member_id) REFERENCES community_members(member_id),   FOREIGN KEY (program_id) REFERENCES outreach_programs(program_id) );

CREATE TABLE community_members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    last_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    address VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE outreach_programs (
    program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    program_description TEXT,
    program_date DATE,
    program_coordinator VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE program_participants (
    participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_id INT,
    member_id INT,
    registration_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (program_id) REFERENCES outreach_programs(program_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (member_id) REFERENCES community_members(member_id)
);

CREATE TABLE program_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    satisfaction_rating INT,
    feedback_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES program_participants(participant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE community_demographics (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	name VARCHAR(50),
	age INT,
	gender VARCHAR(10),
	occupation VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE outreach_programs (
	program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	program_name VARCHAR(50),
	category VARCHAR(50),
	start_date DATE,
	end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE community_groups (
	group_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	group_name VARCHAR(50),
	location VARCHAR(100),
	group_type VARCHAR(50),
	size INT
)

CREATE TABLE member_relationships (
	relationship_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	member_id INT,
	group_id INT,
	relationship_type VARCHAR(50),
	start_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE program_participation (
	participation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	member_id INT,
	program_id INT,
	enrollment_date DATE,
	status VARCHAR(20)
)
